Left knee neurons  HOXA10      Right knee neurons  HOXA11
Left ankle neurons  HOXC10       Right ankle neurons  HOXC11
Left toe neurons  HOXD11        Right toe neurons  HOXD12
Left trunk neurons  SIM1         Right trunk neurons  SIM2
AD lesions  LRP1
Olfactory pathway  NCAM1
General CNS neurons  MAP2
